{"word":"G642 - ἀπορφανίζω - aporphanízō - ap-or-fan-id'-zo - Take","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπορφανίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aporphanízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-or-fan-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Take</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரிந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to bereave of a parent or parents"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3737 - ὀρφανός - orphanós - or-fan-os'/3737\">G3737</a>; to <i>bereave wholly</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>separate</i> (from intercourse): - take.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}